          },
          "reviewBody": "KIIT WORLD SCHOOL is the best school. My kid is happier in this school then their pervious school. They have accomplished many things. In their, pervious school teachers prioritize only 5_7 students but in this school every children is given an opportunity(but for that to happen children also have to take initiative). So, highly recommend this school.",
